Development Model & Requirements
Chosen Development Model
Development Model: Agile
Justification:
The Agile model was chosen because it supports flexibility, continuous improvement, and effective teamwork. It allows the team to adapt to changes, enhance features over time, and receive feedback throughout the development process.
 
User Requirements
Stakeholders
•	End Users (Adopters): Individuals who want to adopt pets. They can browse, search, book adoption meetings, and list pets.
•	Animal Shelters: Organizations that upload and manage pet listings.
•	Admin: Responsible for managing the platform, users, and pet listings.
User Stories
•	As an adopter, I want to register an account so that I can access adoption features.
•	As an adopter, I want to log in so that I can manage my profile and activities.
•	As an adopter, I want to view pet details so that I can learn more before adopting.
•	As an adopter, I want to save pets to favorites so that I can review them later.
•	As an adopter, I want to book an adoption appointment so that I can meet the pet in person.
•	As an adopter, I want to leave reviews so that I can share my experience with others.
•	As an adopter, I want to read reviews so that I can trust shelters or pet owners.
•	As an adopter, I want to see ratings so that I can choose reliable shelters.
•	As an adopter, I want to make donations so that I can help animals in need.
•	As an adopter, I want to view events so that I can attend adoption fairs or meetups.
 
Functional Requirements
Description
•	The system shall allow users to register with a name, email, and password.
•	The system shall allow users to log in and log out.
•	The system shall validate user email and password (minimum 8 characters including a number).
•	The system shall provide a real-time search bar for pets.
•	The system shall allow users to sort results (Newest, Name A–Z).
•	The system shall display pets in a grid layout.
•	The system shall allow users to view detailed information about a pet.
•	The system shall display pet details (age, breed, health, story).
•	The system shall allow users to save pets to Favorites.
•	The system shall allow users to book an adoption appointment.
•	The system shall provide a calendar for selecting date and time.
•	The system shall store and display user bookings.
•	The system shall allow users to add and read reviews.
•	The system shall display ratings for shelters or owners.
•	The system shall allow users to make donations.
•	The system shall manage events (adoption fairs, meetups).
•	The system shall allow users to RSVP to events.
•	The system shall allow users to update their profile.
•	The system shall send and display notifications.
•	The system shall notify users about new pet listings or updates.
