Project Details
Problem Statement
Many people want to adopt pets but struggle to find reliable information about available animals and how to contact shelters or individuals offering pets for adoption. This makes the adoption process more difficult and slows down the chances of animals finding a home.
Proposed Solution
The Pet Adoption Platform is a digital platform that connects people who want to adopt pets with shelters or individuals who have animals available for adoption. The platform allows users to browse pets, view detailed information, and contact the responsible person easily.
Project Aim
The aim of this project is to develop a platform that simplifies the pet adoption process and helps animals find safe and loving homes.
Project Objectives
•	Create a user-friendly platform for pet adoption.
•	Allow shelters or individuals to list pets available for adoption.
•	Provide detailed information and photos for each pet.
•	Allow users to search and filter pets.
•	Enable communication between adopters and pet owners.

